race.comment: DIDWEWIN (6) has returned in terrific order this campaign and really should have more than one win beside her name. Draws to get every chance again and only needs to hold her current level to be right in the finish. FRANCE'S BOY (1) just keeps turning up. At start 163 he's still racing with trademark honesty and is sure to give another bold sight rolling along near the speed. JOVIALE (10) took a big step forward third-up when missing by a lip here. Strips fitter again and has more to offer. BONA FIDE STAR (8) hasn't fired in his last two at headquarters but this is a far more suitable assignment. Draws to get the gun run and is among the winning hopes. BLACK BUGATTI (3) was a determined winner fresh and showed signs of life again here last start. Can build on that and shouldn't be underestimated.
